name: Pemandian Tirta Ujung
address: GJPG+FCF, Jl. Karangasem - Seraya, Karangasem, Kec. Karangasem, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80811, Indonesia
review 1: Not being overrated but when the sun decided to shine brighter than usual, our to go is always Tirta Ujung. Clean, natural pool, friendly staff, the must is its affordable! We love to just swimming slowly while enjoying the breeze and floating üòÖ
review 2: Natural pool with clear water and fish where locals go with their family!
review 3: Wonderful 5k rup natural spring water pool.. There's a warung but no food, just snacks..
review 4: Nice natural spring with clear water and fish in it. Not a one tourist on our visit, only some locals. We visited with our driver. We were said the locals believed it is the "fertility spring" and pairs that have trouble conceiving are coming to bathe in it. ‚ò∫Ô∏è
review 5: I came here before sunset.. it sooo prettyyyyy >ww

name: Two Smiling Buddhas
address: Seraya 2 Jalan Raya Ujung Jasri, Amlapura, Karangasem, Kec. Karangasem, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80811, Indonesia
review 1: This place was awesome!! Just perfect! The villa is decorated in a very "trendy" Balinese style, which is not too much, just feels authentic! There are only 3 accommodations so you almost feel like you have your own private pool! Very quiet area and good food prepared by Ketut! Thank you
review 2:
Amazing quite place, clean houses with bathroom outside, very friendly staff lady who helps you with everything.
Big choose of breakfast options.
Go there and have a chilling time around the nature.
review 4: Nice place..beautifull villa. You should come again.
review 5:
Would not recommend for a solo traveller.
Very absent staff.

name: Villa limun en Limun Guesthouse
address: Jl. Kihajar Dewantara Jasri, Karangasem, Kec. Karangasem, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali, Indonesia
review 1: Absolutely lovely place to unwind. Beautifully landscaped, surrounded by rice fields with the sounds of water running through the property. Views of Agung from everywhere and sea views from the second story. The staff was so nice and accommodating, they really care about their guests. It is new and very clean. Easy walk to a Warang. Breakfast included with your stay. Beautiful morning walk through rice fields. The pool was great and perfect spot to lounge and enjoy the atmosphere and take in the views. I  highly recommend it and will return.
review 2: Very nice modern and clean accommodation with a great breakfast. We also made use of the pool on multiple occasions. Would only recommend staying here if you have a scooter as there isn't much close by. Unfortunately we had to use taxis to get around and the staff were trying to pressure us into using a driver friend of theirs, which made our stay slightly uncomfortable.
review 3:
Stayed three nights and then extended.  New property with ocean and rice field view.   Very comfortable bed, (slept like a baby) fresh, clean rooms and large bathroom.  Sea breeze wafting through the front door.  I'll be back for sure.  Water Palace and Amlapura only 5 minutes away.
Very quiet and night and staff provided everything you want.  Highly recommended for fussy travellers like me.
review 4: The room is beautiful and clean. The furniture is new. There is a nice garden and a big swimming pool. Very friendly staff.

name: Waroeng Nusantara Jasri
address: Jl. Karangasem - Seraya, Karangasem, Kec. Karangasem, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali, Indonesia
review 1:
This is another "Hidden Gems" BBQ Pork Bone Ribs. Perfect combination with "sambal" and vegetable. Also very reasonable price.
You must try this BBQ Pork Bone Ribs / BBQ Iga Babi Bakar, i think this is the best seller menu.

Surely i Will visit this Restaurant again when stay/visit Amlapura areas
review 2:
Very nice and quiet, view on the rice paddock.
Good price, good quantity and beautiful juice !
If you are around have a stop there !
review 3: Good food, non-halal (contains pork), prices are cheap. I ordered pork ribs, fried rice, fried noodle, fried chicken. As for the drinks I ordered fruit ice and "es campur". I think the food and drink are homemade but it tastes delicious. About this place location, it is located near a rice field so you get quiet a good view. There are also lots of small birds in this place so you will hear them singing while you eat. Definitely recommend you to come hereüëå‚ú®
review 4:
For us this place is good with the prices they offer. Recommended  for Pork Ribs, Grill chicken with honey and fried noodle .
The staff is kind and very helpful.
review 5: Fantastic ikan laut pepes & sate, prices are great, the staff are super friendly and the location is peaceful. Happy to find this place! Instagram: @fulltimejwalker
